{"tid":530130,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 關於籃球兄弟情的主題曲 ] 籃球場上一世","createTime":"2018-01-15T13:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T15:19:39.000Z","uid":47374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d9b2c5db4fe5255b1dfce7201b2ede534e97ee","tid":530130,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:03:25.000Z","msg":"因為籃球，很多人當了一生兄弟<br />\n希望我地有機會一齊鬥波鬥到老，好波！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/210003_73781901885850b64b3356ef54a0e20d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F210003_73781901885850b64b3356ef54a0e20d.png&h=196bbe03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1957968011122834/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frealcoach%2Fvideos%2F1957968011122834%2F&d=HW7sH8%2FlW9AFzI22btbTk9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=63551733\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1957968011122834/</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------<br />\n<br />\n原：蠟筆小新-夕陽下的春日部男孩片尾曲<br />\n詞：正宗教練<br />\n唱：正宗教練、鄭世豪、Pennyccw、柒菇碌叔叔<br />\n演：鄭世豪、陳少邦、Brian 陳安立(Viutv)、Pennyccw、喬靖夫、Ernest Chan、Elson 何振然、三言、Jonathan、阿發<br />\n<br />\n約定放工 拎起個波 跟兩隊再 全力發威<br />\n籃球令我得到兄弟<br />\n大個咗都可以一齊<br />\n行埋落去 球場上再繼續嚟<br />\n<br />\n往日唔怕高手 將佢地砌低<br />\n前日我醫生講 你做乜身體咁虧<br />\n照舊陪你征戰籃球場上一世<br />\n無懼爆入嚟 撞到死咁濟 但趺打好貴<br />\n<br />\n當初超fit 嚟手佢又入五六球<br />\n依家OT 佢仲未走<br />\n意外再生多個 日日起身都諗買樓<br />\n即管今晚 等我地拯救<br />\n<br />\n被困感覺我受夠 攰到嘔泡繼續鬥<br />\n今晚我 得到  無盡嘅自由<br />\n滴晒汗 陪住你 揮灑幾個街頭<br />\n期望到老咗  人面照舊<br />\n<br />\n帶住肥腩奔跑 雙腳就快跛<br />\n憑默契 一開火 爆廿一分比你睇<br />\nChok住條氣 打到凌晨時份都制<br />\n贏就繼續嚟 硬上啦契弟<br />\n<br />\n某日行到終點 郁下又趺低<br />\n期望我啲孫仔 有勒邦占士咁威<br />\n幸慶同你 拎個籃球維繫一世<br />\n強敵殺入嚟 狀態幾咁弊 亦要狠狠砌"},{"pid":"146c044e9cdee6c2b8038057df398357f6caa653","tid":530130,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:07:43.000Z","msg":"自pish"},{"pid":"f76cadf7728dfa2bab19ceba3dadd4f91ddc0498","tid":530130,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"自pish"},{"pid":"ec0de046a44b28c3eff1b18b64738584156f7e87","tid":530130,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"自peace"},{"pid":"e7c36ecedc580a3fd7bdece8ccefa357a86da891","tid":530130,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"自park"},{"pid":"30267a82b493f3bcea3c17e20b5accc8fe660c8b","tid":530130,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd18f6f2e8f97841a2e6df97338ffcbcd6b4981","tid":530130,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30267a82b493f3bcea3c17e20b5accc8fe660c8b","tid":530130,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"山兄"},{"pid":"f0933286b58b6fefafd9d397c740e7b9acf42814","tid":530130,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"自pure"},{"pid":"fce2b965d4524438b2dc4adfb31a6cd6056fe794","tid":530130,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:57:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7c7d3636723804e579cf370725d7f8f956ff6c29","tid":530130,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9fc39e8dccf836bf19c70f87979423a1b0ea57a5","tid":530130,"uid":72414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" clas